<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>About Us - HarmonyHub</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/CSS/about.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/CSS/headerL.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/CSS/bodyL.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/CSS/fonts.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Matemasie&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Dancing+Script:wght@400..700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    {{>headerL}}
    <section class="about">
        <div class="intro">
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p>Welcome to HarmonyHub, your gateway to vibrant communities and shared passions!</p>
        </div>

        <section class="mission-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>Our mission is simple: <strong>to empower creators and communities</strong>. We aim to provide a platform that allows individuals to express themselves, grow their passions, and engage with others who share similar interests. Whether you’re an artist, entrepreneur, foodie, spiritual seeker, or bookworm, HarmonyHub is your place to connect, learn, and grow.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="why-harmonyhub-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 align="center">Why HarmonyHub?</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Creator Empowerment:</strong> We provide tools and features that allow creators to showcase their work, build their communities, and interact with their audience in meaningful ways.</li>
                    <li><strong>Inclusive Communities:</strong> From art to entrepreneurship, food, spirituality, and beyond—our platform is home to a diverse range of communities that cater to your passions.</li>
                    <li><strong>User-Centric Experience:</strong> HarmonyHub offers a seamless, intuitive experience tailored to your preferences.</li>
                    <li><strong>Exclusive and Public Content:</strong> Discover exclusive content from creators or dive into the public feed to explore new ideas, insights, and connections.</li>
                    <li><strong>Engagement-Driven Features:</strong> Participate in discussions, share your creations, host events, and collaborate with others to build something extraordinary together.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="values-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 align="center">Our Values</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Collaboration:</strong> We encourage collaboration among creators and members to foster a spirit of teamwork and creativity.</li>
                    <li><strong>Diversity:</strong> We celebrate diverse perspectives and believe that everyone has something unique to contribute.</li>
                    <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> We are committed to transparency and building a trustworthy environment for our users.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="join-us-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Join Us on the Journey</h2>
                <p>We invite you to be part of HarmonyHub and experience the joy of connecting with communities that reflect your passions. Whether you’re here to discover or create, your journey begins with HarmonyHub.</p>
                <p><strong>Let’s build, create, and grow—together.</strong></p>
                <a href="/signup" class="join-button">Join Now</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </section>
    




</body>
</html>
